Class KmsKeyName (2.9.0)

This class identifies a Google Cloud KMS Key.

A KMS key is identified by its project_id, location, key_ring, and kms_key_name.

Note: This class makes no effort to validate the components of the key, It is the application's responsibility to provide a valid project id, location, key ring, and KMS key name. Passing invalid values will not be checked until the key is used in a RPC.
See https://cloud.google.com/kms/docs for more information on KMS.
